{"tid":1905662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[眾籌] 元朗9月21號至今還押>150日 被控暴動既手足 要幫手","createTime":"2020-03-01T11:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T06:57:33.000Z","uid":334720,"like":38,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"c7a37bcc8006a1acce6c3deecc7c622ce0ac9dce","tid":1905662,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:52:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gogetfunding.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/6512354/img/mimg_6512354_1582926063-630x330.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F6512354%2Fimg%2Fmimg_6512354_1582926063-630x330.jpg&h=2c041360&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌LINK</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/neverforget/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fneverforget%2F&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGokyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=4e123b6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/neverforget/</a><br />\n&quot;去年9月21日元朗恐襲兩個月，網民發起到元朗靜坐，及後演變成衝突，有多人被「私了」，其中兩名男子分別被控襲擊致造成身體傷害及有意圖而傷人等罪。事隔4個月，控方今加控二人暴動等罪，並再起訴多一人，與二人案件合併，3人共被控8項控罪。案件押後至3月18日再訊，以待控方準備轉介文件，移交區域法院處理。<br />\n<br />\n首被告張裕泰面對各一項「襲擊致造成身體傷害」、「非法禁錮」、「暴動」及「刑事損壞」罪；次被告陳澧圖被控各一項「參與非法集結」、「暴動」、「刑事損壞」及「有意圖而傷人」罪；第三被告羅同學面對一項「參與非法集結」及兩項「刑事損壞」罪。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n致各位手足:<br />\n<br />\n 本次眾籌為張裕泰先生之母親黃女仕發起，張裕泰先生於去年9月21日元朗恐襲兩周月靜坐活動中被捕，至今一直被還押已超過150日，在羈留所中渡過生日、聖誕及新年。期間案件不停押後，對當事人及其家庭造成沉重的精神及經濟壓力。<br />\n<br />\n 當事人家景並不富裕，亦感激612基金一直的支援，惟龐大的法律開支亦令612無法全數資助，其家庭在墊底5個月後亦感到經濟壓力。而法庭方面一直無辦法成功申請保釋，如今更被加控暴動罪，故此決定發起眾籌希望能夠積沙成塔幫助其家庭解決目前困境。<br />\n<br />\n 而眾籌所得金額會全數存入律師行，交由律師行托管，黃女仕亦與律師行簽定法律文件，該金額只會用作官司用途，若有餘額將會全數捐贈612基金希望能夠幫助更多人。<br />\n<br />\n 雖然有關張裕泰之報導不多，但希望大家可以略盡綿力，毋忘各位為香港付出之手足。<br />\n<br />\n如有任何查詢可以透過telegram: @nreadd (所有家屬證明，法律證明文件)<br />\n<br />\n有關之報導:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1070158\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1070158&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGokyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=8167f9c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1070158&h=281b5d1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1070158</a>"},{"pid":"018759d7b303d70b85a195e8c8a6c394bef206e2","tid":1905662,"uid":77937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:52:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db347a1459b81f506ac0a14a57f4030137ee8ab6","tid":1905662,"uid":31952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:53:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"505dea0a7c17de6714898ca0fcd427f46fa0e6f9","tid":1905662,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:53:17.000Z","msg":"仲無得保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36a329024bbe7cc961a161bcc61ede2e683dc6f","tid":1905662,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:54:33.000Z","msg":"而家仲未保到釋呀<br />\n<br />\n3月18號再審 一陣又黎要幾十萬保釋金 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊度有咁撚多錢呀?<br />\n<br />\n課到幾多得幾多, 18號前要籌到100%呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c6c6f1cd45f5509a2040b20454fda18d4ecfc73","tid":1905662,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:57:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17953dfd09990f51d96db46faa852bf43de13c22","tid":1905662,"uid":54965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:58:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5fc3044f25a3f69a52b2b4fb1e38f74b4d9d039c","tid":1905662,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:58:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8041b5c206539c18e60a25af497ea1be0795ea9b","tid":1905662,"uid":96158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a01eb0036ffc6bf749b0f5869da002ef52a5ed","tid":1905662,"uid":8566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:00:27.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"3e531918f3b236f564375bc85931f458db349414","tid":1905662,"uid":200532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:31:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4832f288e640aa4e30f6d2ef3ab4d9a177c25e72","tid":1905662,"uid":152810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:32:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5c50c4f08d373085881ad2cf2e8a778515137ce","tid":1905662,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:33:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3df239d5aeacdb5c48d9e0cf62c2d92de6874764","tid":1905662,"uid":259216,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:34:35.000Z","msg":"點解612會比唔到錢佢 唔係收咗好多又用得少㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca8507cd8911f6e238751528d1d2fe871340caa","tid":1905662,"uid":334720,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3df239d5aeacdb5c48d9e0cf62c2d92de6874764","tid":1905662,"uid":259216,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:34:35.000Z","msg":"點解612會比唔到錢佢 唔係收咗好多又用得少㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T13:45:50.000Z","msg":"因為每個case有限額<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">當事人家景並不富裕，亦感激612基金一直的支援，惟龐大的法律開支亦令612無法全數資助</span>"},{"pid":"67ff3c69f4c2cefa4850deff5db0caa2765c81d5","tid":1905662,"uid":24613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T15:35:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52df13477446d5